><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108246\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108246)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108246)\">Matt. 25:31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113859\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113859)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113859)\">D&amp;C 45:44<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110025\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110025)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110025)\">1 Tim. 5:22<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">24. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113432\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113432)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113432)\">D&amp;C 24:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114686\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114686)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114686)\">D&amp;C 84:33<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114874\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114874)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114874)\">D&amp;C 88:80<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">25. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116973\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116973)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116973)\">Abr. 1:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">26. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109355\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109355)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109355)\">Rom. 11:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111358\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111358)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111358)\">Jacob 1:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114270\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114270)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114270)\">D&amp;C 66:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">27. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115476\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115476)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115476)\">D&amp;C 107:39<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113268\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113268)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113268)\">D&amp;C 18:32<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">28. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112977\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112977)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112977)\">Moro. 8:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">29. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110041\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110041)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110041)\">2 Tim. 2:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">30. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110827\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110827)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110827)\">Rev. 17:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}